{
  "stem": "6195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were in Wieliczka, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was-- my husband was there, and I was there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, at that time, we were not married.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we knew each other from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we worked at-- as I said, I worked carrying furniture and washing dishes and whatnot, and sometimes I had a turn in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I was in the kitchen, the butcher was bringing the meat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was friendly, so I was friendly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one day-- but I can't really remember whether we were there three months, four months, two months-- I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One day, he came and he said, you know, the word is going around that they're going to finish you off-- from here take you to somewhere where they finish off people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't really know what he meant by finishing off people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he said, I don't know either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there is a camp somewhere, where the people go in and never come out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, why are you telling me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, well, what can I do about it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, look, Christmas is coming up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Christmas Eve, we have Christmas dinner with guests.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'll have music, make loud the music.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you have to make your way, very quietly, to my place-- which he described to me, how I have to go-- and go into the barn.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I must mention, I was petrified of animals, maybe more than meeting a Nazi on the way, because I will drown in the snow and he couldn't probably see me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But an animal together with me in the barn, that was something I couldn't visualize.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But life was at stake.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
